                This callback is invoked just before update of each internal feature (construction feature and output feature) of custom feature.        
                Implementations of this callback should only modify parameters of internal feature for which callback is invoked.
                Implementations of this callback should not:
                    - delete internal features or create new internal feature in this callback.
                    - trigger part save or update from this callback.
                    - log any object to delete or update from this callback.
                    - try to display entities from this callback.
                    - try to launch any user interface from this callback.
                    - createdelete any geometric objects in this callback.
